<span class="line">&#123;% p 样式参数(参数以空格划分), 文本内容 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></details><details><summary style="font-size: larger;">配置参数</summary><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.字体: logo, code</span><br><span class="line">2.颜色: red,yellow,green,cyan,blue,gray</span><br><span class="line">3.大小: small, h4, h3, h2, h1, large, huge, ultra</span><br><span class="line">4.对齐方向: left, center, right</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></details><details><summary style="font-size: larger;">示例源码</summary><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- 彩色文字</span><br><span class="line">在一段话中方便插入各种颜色的标签，包括：&#123;% span red, 红色 %&#125;、&#123;% span yellow, 黄色 %&#125;、&#123;% span green, 绿色 %&#125;、&#123;% span cyan, 青色 %&#125;、&#123;% span blue, 蓝色 %&#125;、&#123;% span gray, 灰色 %&#125;。</span><br><span class="line">- 超大号文字</span><br><span class="line">文档「开始」页面中的标题部分就是超大号文字。</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% span center logo large, Volantis %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% span center small, A Wonderful Theme for Hexo %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></details><h2 id="2-3-段落文本-p"><a href="#2-3-段落文本-p" class="headerlink" title="2.3 段落文本 p"></a>2.3 段落文本 p</h2><details><summary style="font-size: larger;">示例源码</summary><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span